name: Get Detailed Device Location
description: Retrieves the device geolocation retrieved through various means, the coordinates, and engages the user by asking for feedback about their current location.

inputs.description: Maximum random delay set to avoid external API overload. Provide number of seconds lower than 600
inputs.name: MaximumDelayInSeconds

inputs.description: API key to be used for the external Microsoft Bing Maps geolocation service. Provide empty value ("") to skip its retrieval
inputs.name: BingMapsAPIKey

inputs.description: API key to be used for the external IPAPI geolocation service. Provide empty value ("") to skip its retrieval
inputs.name: IPAPIKey

inputs.description: IPAPI HTTPS enabled. Valid values are true/false. This value will be evaluated only if a IPAPI Key was provided
inputs.name: EnableIPAPIHTTPS

inputs.description: ID of the Campaign to be launched. Leave empty if to skip it. Provide empty value ("") to skip its retrieval
inputs.name: LocationFeedbackCampaignId

outputs.description: CSV list with the Bing Maps API location details
outputs.name: BingMapsLocationDetails

outputs.description: CSV list with the IPAPI location details
outputs.name: IPAPILocationDetails

outputs.description: CSV list with the location details provided by the user through the campaign
outputs.name: UserFeedbackLocationDetails
